SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."Description", p."Name", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-17 00:22:30.037 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (46ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."AssetId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", (

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."Description", p."Name", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."Description", p."Name", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", (

    ELSE ''

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."Description", p."Name", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."Description", p."Name", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-17 07:59:07.204 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-17 08:05:32.136 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

2025-10-17 08:09:15.000 +03:00 [INF] CORS policy execution successful.
2025-10-17 08:09:15.000 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (22ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"

    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (

    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"

    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls

                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-17 09:15:42.100 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (67ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

2025-10-17 09:16:32.995 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (34ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0

    FROM "SimCards" AS s

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"

LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"

) AS t

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."SimAccountNo", t."SimServiceNo", t."SimStartDate", t."SimStatus", t."SimSerialNo", p."Name", s0."Name", s1."Name", s2."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SimCardId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT s."Id", s."ProjectId", s."SimAccountNo", s."SimCardPlanId", s."SimProviderId", s."SimSerialNo", s."SimServiceNo", s."SimStartDate", s."SimStatus", s."SimTypeId"
    FROM "SimCards" AS s
    ORDER BY s."SimAccountNo"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimCardPlans" AS s0 ON t."SimCardPlanId" = s0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimProviders" AS s1 ON t."SimProviderId" = s1."Id"
LEFT JOIN "SimTypes" AS s2 ON t."SimTypeId" = s2."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SimCardId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SimCardId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SimCardId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSimCards" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SimCardId"
ORDER BY t."SimAccountNo"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."PoNumber", t."PoDate", t."ExpectedDeliveryDate", t."ActualDeliveryDate", t."Status", (
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(p1."Quantity"::numeric(18,2) * p1."UnitPrice"), 0.0)
    FROM "PurchaseOrderItems" AS p1
    WHERE t."Id" = p1."PurchaseOrderId") AS "TotalAmount", s."Name" AS "SupplierName", p0."Name" AS "ProjectName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "PurchaseOrderItems" AS p2
    WHERE t."Id" = p2."PurchaseOrderId") AS "ItemCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."ActualDeliveryDate", p."CreatedAt", p."ExpectedDeliveryDate", p."PoDate", p."PoNumber", p."ProjectId", p."Status", p."SupplierId"
    FROM "PurchaseOrders" AS p
    ORDER BY p."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
INNER JOIN "Suppliers" AS s ON t."SupplierId" = s."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."PoNumber", t."PoDate", t."ExpectedDeliveryDate", t."ActualDeliveryDate", t."Status", (
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(p1."Quantity"::numeric(18,2) * p1."UnitPrice"), 0.0)
    FROM "PurchaseOrderItems" AS p1
    WHERE t."Id" = p1."PurchaseOrderId") AS "TotalAmount", s."Name" AS "SupplierName", p0."Name" AS "ProjectName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "PurchaseOrderItems" AS p2
    WHERE t."Id" = p2."PurchaseOrderId") AS "ItemCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."ActualDeliveryDate", p."CreatedAt", p."ExpectedDeliveryDate", p."PoDate", p."PoNumber", p."ProjectId", p."Status", p."SupplierId"
    FROM "PurchaseOrders" AS p
    ORDER BY p."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
INNER JOIN "Suppliers" AS s ON t."SupplierId" = s."Id"
INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON t."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
ORDER BY t."CreatedAt" DESC
